OL,3,CITV News on the frontline with police
OL,4,Cdismantling county lines crime networks
OL,6,FITV News London joined police on the
OL,7,Ffrontline as they crack down on county
OL,8,Flines where criminal gangs move drugs
OL,9,Ffrom cities into smaller towns and use
OL,10,Fvulnerable people, often children, to
OL,11,Fsell them.
OL,13,FIn a recent operation, officers
OL,14,Farrested more than 400 people,
OL,15,Frecovered #195,000, and charged 178
OL,16,Fpeople across the capital.
OL,18,FWe joined the Met as teams executed
OL,19,Fthree simultaneous warrants in London,
OL,20,Fwhich police said would have a
OL,21,F"significant impact" on the community.
OL,26,@}D@AOU}D@TO]
