CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1774033868
OL,3,CITV News on the frontline with police
OL,4,Cdismantling county lines crime networks
OL,6,F"Drug activity doesn't work in
OL,7,Fisolation," said Detective Chief
OL,8,FInspector Sarb Kaur.
OL,10,F"It drives antisocial behaviour,
OL,11,Fhomicide, violence and serious harm
OL,12,Fthat is the impact on other crime
OL,13,Ftypes.
OL,15,F"We have put many more resources into
OL,16,Ffrontline policing. I urge communities
OL,17,Fto support us. If you see crime in
OL,18,Fyour area or on your streets, contact
OL,19,Fyour Safer Neighbourhood Teams, call
OL,20,FCrimestoppers and let us know.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@KO]rD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1774033868
OL,3,CITV News on the frontline with police
OL,4,Cdismantling county lines crime networks
OL,6,F"Let's tackle crime networks together,
OL,7,Fbecause only by working with our
OL,8,Fpartners can we dismantle them," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe Met said its operations are not
OL,12,Fjust about enforcement, but also about
OL,13,Fsafeguarding vulnerable people within
OL,14,Fcommunities.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Sarb Kaur
OL,17,Fadded: "They are the ones suffering
OL,18,Fbehind closed doors. It's really
OL,19,Fimportant that we support and
OL,20,Funderstand them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]yD@HOU|D@QO]
