OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1774033868
OL,3,CITV News on the frontline with police
OL,4,Cdismantling county lines crime networks
OL,6,FCounty lines activity has serious
OL,7,Fimpacts on individuals, families and
OL,8,Fcommunities, increasing crime and
OL,9,Fputting young people at risk of harm.
OL,11,FThe Met has specialist teams working
OL,12,Facross London to engage with children
OL,13,Fand steer them away from crime.
OL,15,FAsked what difference the arrests
OL,16,Fwould make, Detective Chief Inspector
OL,17,FSarb Kaur said: "This has made a huge
OL,18,Fdent in the community here.
OL,26,@yD@QOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
