OL,3,CITV News on the frontline with police
OL,4,Cdismantling county lines crime networks
OL,6,F"My proactive teams are relentless in
OL,7,Fdeveloping intelligence. They act on
OL,8,Fit to disrupt and dismantle organised
OL,9,Fcrime groups and you can see the
OL,10,Fimpact in communities today."
